input.activity_signal: Company was acquired by RealPage on January 4, 2021 according to Business Wire press release found in web search. No recent FCC filings (latest was 2020-05-29). While web presence exists via whitesky.us website and LinkedIn profile, the acquisition suggests the company no longer operates as an independent entity.
input.product_summary: WhiteSky Communications provided managed telecommunications services including bulk Internet, cable TV, and VoIP phone services primarily to multifamily properties, student housing, hotels, and assisted living facilities.
